snippet.title: IS AMBER HEARD SUPER EMPOWERED AND KICKASS?// PARODY VIDEO
snippet.description:
Hi guys! I hope you are doing great today! 
My name is Carla Yang and welcome to my channel. 

Todays video is an Amber Heard parody, created for entertainment purposes only. I’ve used several sources as references for this one parody if you'd like to check them out!
Also I am so sorry I didn’t post a video last Wednesday, life got a bit hectic! I will be posting fridays for the next few weeks!

Disclaimer: This video was created for entertainment purposes only.
This video does not intend to make fun of alcoholism or alcoholics in any way, it is mentioned in the video because it seems that alcohol is a huge part of Ambers lifestyle choices, there is more information about that at the end of the video. 

Also this video does not intend to offend anyones lifestyles choices.
All information used is alleged.

CHECK THESE ARTICLES IF YOU WISH:
https://poptopic.com.au/lifestyle/celebrities/rumour-amber-heard-is-a-messy-drunk-and-violent-alcoholic-pics/

https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-9938021/Amber-Heard-steps-wine-run-ex-Johnny-Depp-continues-50-million-libel-law-suit.html#reader-comments

https://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-1263981/Amber-Heard-My-baby-357-magnum.html


VIDEOS:
Next source is this video reference and is long, so if you like to just watch the actual part I took inspiration from, make sure to watch around the 2:29 mark, where the Loreal promo is shown.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Klv09j42dS8&list=PL3b067p5TTpNZHhd3zAdy1I3Esjp8zu6p&index=19&t=157s

In this interview Amber talks about “empowered” women and the same old jazz she always talks about in her Loreal interview. 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P6rJA7jXx-U

#amberheard #johnnydepp #loreal

Hope you like this video! And if you do, don't forget to let me know your thoughts, like and subscribe! :D
Please stay safe out there and stay tuned, my name is Carla Yang, see you soon!
